OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775631893
OL,3,CPrice of first class stamp increases
OL,4,Cto #1.80
OL,6,FThe price of stamps has risen again,
OL,7,Fwith the cost of a first class stamp
OL,8,Fjumping by 10p to #1.80.
OL,10,FThe increase came into effect on
OL,11,FTuesday despite repeated failures by
OL,12,FRoyal Mail to meet its delivery
OL,13,Ftargets and amid growing concerns over
OL,14,Fthe performance of the service.
OL,16,FThe price of a second class stamp has
OL,17,Frisen by 4p to 91p.
OL,19,FStamps bought before the price
OL,20,Fincrease will remain valid and can
OL,21,Fstill be used for postage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
