OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775631893
OL,3,CPrice of first class stamp increases
OL,4,Cto #1.80
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe increase means the cost of a first
OL,12,Fclass stamp has now more than doubled,
OL,13,Fgoing up by 137% in the past six
OL,14,Fyears, after eight increases, while
OL,15,Fthe cost of a second class stamp has
OL,16,Fbeen hiked six times.
OL,18,FThe latest increase comes after Royal
OL,19,FMail said in February that it had
OL,20,Fmissed delivery targets once again in
OL,21,Fthe most recent quarter.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
