FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775631893
OL,3,CPrice of first class stamp increases
OL,4,Cto #1.80
OL,6,FAnnouncing the decision last month,
OL,7,FRoyal Mail said the price change
OL,8,Freflected the continued rise in the
OL,9,Fcost of delivery as letter volumes
OL,10,Ffell and the number of addresses
OL,11,Fsurged.
OL,13,FRichard Travers, managing director of
OL,14,Fletters at Royal Mail, said: "We
OL,15,Falways consider price changes very
OL,16,Fcarefully, balancing affordability
OL,17,Fwith the rising cost of delivering
OL,18,Fmail.
OL,26,@vD@^OU
