OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775631893
OL,3,CPrice of first class stamp increases
OL,4,Cto #1.80
OL,6,F"On average, UK adults now spend just
OL,7,F#6.50 each year on stamps and there
OL,8,Fare 70% fewer letters sent than 20
OL,9,Fyears ago.
OL,11,F"In the meantime, the number of
OL,12,Faddresses we deliver to has increased
OL,13,Fby four million to 32 million
OL,14,Faddresses across the UK."
OL,16,FThe last time Royal Mail met its
OL,17,Fannual target for delivering first
OL,18,Fclass post on time was in 2019-20.
